# Performance Rules

Budget: **LCP ≤ 2.5 s · TBT = 0 · CLS = 0**

## Images

- Always set `width` + `height` on `<img>` to prevent CLS.
- Above-fold images: `loading="eager"` + `<link rel="preload">` in `<head>`.
- Below-fold images: `loading="lazy"`.
- Serve images no larger than their rendered size; use `srcset` for responsive.

## JavaScript

- Zero JS on initial page load is the default.
- Choose the weakest `client:*` directive that satisfies the use case:
  `client:idle` > `client:visible` > `client:load` > `client:only`.

## Fonts

- Self-host in `public/fonts/`; use `font-display: swap`.
- Include only required weights and subsets.

## CSS

- Tailwind purge must be active in production.
- No inline `style` attributes with layout-affecting properties unless unavoidable.

## Checklist before committing a component

- [ ] No new JS bundle introduced unintentionally
- [ ] Images have dimensions
- [ ] No render-blocking `<link>` or `<script>` added to `<head>`
